{"tid":1674615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城大校方打壓「城大和你傾」","createTime":"2019-10-25T10:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T01:12:09.000Z","uid":107092,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6e2232dee9794ee43a4a7640ec07f5bc0fa0a3","tid":1674615,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"擅自於10月29日在城大舉辦論壇的傳言<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n各位同事、同學和校友：<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n大學留意到近日網上流傳將於下星期二（10月29日）傍晚在王氏國際廣場舉辦論壇。對於有校外人士聲稱將於城大校園舉行論壇，大學深表關注。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n我們必須澄清以下各點：<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n 1 大學不是該未經申請活動的主辦機構；<br />\n 2 該未經申請活動擬使用的地點，早已被預留當天作校內活動用途；<br />\n 3 大學有既定程序及機制供本校教職員及學生申請使用場地。而在使用大學設施的守則中，已清楚列明校園內不可以進行任何商業、政治、牟利及個人活動。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n我們非常關注當晚如有大量校外人士擅自聚集校園進行未經申請活動，勢必嚴重影響校園的正常運作及教學活動。同時，屆時一旦出現突發事故或混亂情況，大學亦沒有足夠人手作出人群管理及應變。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n大學恪守自主、保持中立，並不支持任何個人的特定政治觀點，亦非政治角力的場所。我們呼籲大學社群內的每一位為此付出努力，校外人士不得干擾大學，更不應該進入校園干擾大學的正常運作。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n大學對任何人士闖入校園舉辦或參與未經批准的活動保留追究的權利。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n傳訊及公關處啟<br />\n2019年10月25日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpJxeWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpJxeWy.jpg&h=70936021&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83e801828e480be281ec648be00ccc8b96e51d04","tid":1674615,"uid":107092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"shittyU"},{"pid":"8afb609c91960c10faa05b079adb33d48f3d7526","tid":1674615,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e619aa52425b70db0346dd88f1da186c032c1061","tid":1674615,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dc7c66368ffdbff3efc6580dde6db1a73d909f7","tid":1674615,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92146f19e71b5aab54c2e5f868824a6b03e6ce20","tid":1674615,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a67d0de8154ed2639aaa3d8e52207995f103e50f","tid":1674615,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"個論壇標題就係言論自由，shity就自己示範點樣打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e794e904e9ec59ba3553be6834f1647d812fdaf","tid":1674615,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"又一城市大學"},{"pid":"86194ca78791f71c11a3f2f57f1a5ee878054f0f","tid":1674615,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14b7659718ea77c048ad9f8e68474d93f7fb22ab","tid":1674615,"uid":197149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"「不支持任何個人的特定政治觀點，亦非政治角力的場所」<br />\n<br />\n咁你立即執撚咗成個政政佢啦"},{"pid":"ac030cf4df3fecf76853aec6a9500d11910d604b","tid":1674615,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d06819de3e16be0d7f1b165c9ebf89e08939a8a","tid":1674615,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cd7ea8250453fa9cfef2eeea44aebd61c4b632f","tid":1674615,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:03:25.000Z","msg":"郭位死左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cb1a6876c8c4772af5ca96875ba72fc8cb1ecd","tid":1674615,"uid":313040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"I didn't know there would be any event on the 29th of October. Now I know. I may go hahaha"},{"pid":"3bf66e3c1ff95fc35884dbb57b429338b7949acc","tid":1674615,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e893e0484a2f6e5aa11d8190f771caa28b72b2a6","tid":1674615,"uid":166659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci